snippet.title: Gallery of Things: Reveries Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Gallery of Things: Reveries" invites players into a surreal world where Dadaism meets hidden object gameplay. Across 36 levels, experience a thought-provoking montage of images that challenge your perceptions of nature and technology. Each level is a unique puzzle, blending art with mystery, and leading players on an introspective journey. Discover hidden items and explore the intricate relationship between humanity, nature, and technology.

Available for Game Club members on December 12th, 2023.

https://www.bigfishgames.com
